<ul>
<li><a href="http://amodernstory.com/2014/09/23/installing-hadoop-on-mac-osx-yosemite/">installing-hadoop-on-mac-osx-yosemite</a>， 完全照着装的。</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>简单的代码：

<ul>
